commit_list.repo_description: A remote-hg mirror of Mercurial itself. This clone was performed using the remote-hg that was gracelessly killed off by an out-of-control Git contributor (but is still used here): 'git clone hg::http://scelenic.com/hg'. It should be updated every 15 minutes via a cronjob.
